ombic structure of magnetite below the Verwey transition. When applying\na magnetic field of 5 T the system shows an induced negative thermal expansion\nin the intermediate magnetic phase as observed in ZnCr$_2$Se$_4$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 19 Nov 2008 11:06:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
